descriptionHtml:
This is a joke mod which changes the name of all horkers to "Wordbanks", made on request.

[url=http://knowyourmeme.com/memes/wordbank-walrus]http://knowyourmeme.com/memes/wordbank-walrus[/url]

WordBank (Walrus) is an internet meme which started as an in-joke on Reddit inspired by a photograph of a preschooler’s incorrect response to an English vocabulary quiz misidentifying a drawing of Walrus as a “word bank,” a term used to indicate the portion of the prompt listing all answer choices in a test.

Not just content with changing the names of the animals themselves, I've also changed other items so you can now have "Wordbank Stew", "Wordbank Tusks", etc. Plus the book "Wordbank Attacks" with all necessary changes to the text.

Images above uploaded to Reddit by gynoceros - their usage here is presumed to be fair use.
author: jackstarr
